director; with Barbara Hershey, Robbie Coltrane, Lisa Marie, Debi
Mazar, John Leguizano, Clarence Williams 3d, Nick Chindlund, Mike
Starr, Harry Hamlin. Reviewed by Lawrence Van Gelder.
</P>
<P>
   LETTER-FILM-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``The Love Letter'': Peter Chan,
director; with Kate Capshaw, Gloria Stuart, Ellen DeGeneres.
Reviewed by Stehen Holden.
