<P>
   BC-COSMETICS-MARKETPLACE-NYT (moved on Thursday, May 20)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Thursday, May 20,
about efforts to sell Revlon misidentified the owner of a possible
buyer, Coty. It is a unit of Joh. A. Benckiser G.m.b.H., not
Benckiser N.V.
