<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-FUNDS-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
ATTN EDITORS:  

</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   The spot budget story FUNDS-DECLINE (f) will not move in
tonight's Boston Globe file.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
