<P>
   The New York Times News Service will send the following Money
and Business articles for release Sunday, May 23, 1999:
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR; ELIMINATE: INVEST-AD-STOCKS and BIZ-HOTELS-WIRED. ADD:
CREDITCARDS-COMPETITION, BIZ-TRACTORS and BIZ-PENNIES.
</P>
